Durban - Minister in the Presidency Jeff Radebe says
there is no contradiction between radical economic transformation and inclusive
growth. Radebe was speaking to IOL on the sidelines of the World
Economic Forum Africa at the ICC in Durban on Wednesday. "There is no contradiction. If you look at
governments National Development Plan and all the other policies put in place
then you will see that they complement each other," said Radebe. He added that the World Economic Forum Africa taking
place in Durban would showcase South Africa to potential investors across the
globe.  To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
